\b0 I think this is the only project in the series that will slow down and eventually die if you leave it running. I am constantly creating crystal shards and no cap has been put into place. So if you leave it running and go to the grocery store, Don't be surprised if you come back to a melted computer, dead houseplants, and severely pissed off neighbors and/or cats.\

\b \

